snippet.title: Wizard Cats Teaser Trailer
snippet.description: Wizard Cats is an innovative roguelite dungeon crawler featuring a groundbreaking spellcrafting system. Players take on the role of a cat thrown into a magical realm, where they must craft powerful spells to survive and conquer ever-changing challenges. You can follow Wizard Cats’ development on Discord (https://discord.gg/wizardcats) and wishlist the game on Steam (https://store.steampowered.com/app/3176500/Wizard_Cats/) to receive updates and announcements.
